dct_description_sm: Map shows roads, terrain, and notable features. Relief shown by 10 feet contour interval, partially by form lines, and spot heights. Depth shown by isolines and fathoms. Includes guide to numbered features, index to streets, boundaries map, and overprint legend. Map shows evacuation route Kampala- Entebbe. "Map information as of 1990." "Warning: The magenta overprint shows selected revision only and may be incomplete in both content and areas covered." ©Copyright 1994 by the United States Government.
